x&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_is_background_backdrop&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_is_background_on_scroll&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_link_sidemenu&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_link_fullmenu&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_link_closed_fullmenu&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_is_sticky&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_is_fadeout_animation&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_mobile_static&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-526aa19 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"526aa19\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;grandtour_ext_link_sidemenu&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_link_fullmenu&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_link_closed_fullmenu&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_is_sticky&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_is_scrollme&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_is_smoove&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_is_parallax_mouse&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_is_infinite&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_is_fadeout_animation&quot;:&quot;false&quot;,&quot;grandtour_ext_mobile_static&quot;:&quot;false&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 data-start=\"625\" data-end=\"936\">Taj Rishikesh Resort &amp; Spa\u00a0<\/h4><p data-start=\"625\" data-end=\"936\"><em data-start=\"658\" data-end=\"684\">Singthali, near Shivpuri<\/em><br data-start=\"684\" data-end=\"687\" \/>This luxury resort is located about 30 km from Rishikesh town, away from the crowd, right next to the Ganga river. Rooms have forest or river views, and it\u2019s a great pick for wellness getaways\u2014there\u2019s a full spa, yoga pavilion, and riverside deck.<\/p><p data-start=\"939\" data-end=\"997\"><strong data-start=\"939\" data-end=\"951\">Best for<\/strong>: Couples, wellness travelers, peace seekers<br \/><strong data-start=\"1000\" data-end=\"1016\">Approx Price<\/strong>: \u20b920,000\u2013\u20b935,000\/night<br \/><strong data-start=\"1044\" data-end=\"1060\">Good to Know<\/strong>: Limited phone network; ideal for digital detox<\/p><h4 data-start=\"1117\" data-end=\"1411\">The Naini Retreat, Nainital\u00a0<\/h4><p data-start=\"1117\" data-end=\"1411\"><em data-start=\"1151\" data-end=\"1178\">Ayarpata Slopes, Nainital<\/em><br data-start=\"1178\" data-end=\"1181\" \/>Originally a royal residence, now a heritage-style hotel with modern upgrades. Just a 10-minute drive from Mall Road but feels private and calm. Rooms have wooden interiors, and there\u2019s a great view of Naini Lake from the lawns.<\/p><p data-start=\"1414\" data-end=\"1470\"><strong data-start=\"1414\" data-end=\"1426\">Best for<\/strong>: Couples, small families, heritage lovers<br \/><strong data-start=\"1473\" data-end=\"1489\">Approx Price<\/strong>: \u20b910,000\u2013\u20b918,000\/night<br \/><strong data-start=\"1517\" data-end=\"1533\">Good to Know<\/strong>: Gets sold out on weekends and holidays; book early<\/p><h4 data-start=\"1594\" data-end=\"1894\">JW Marriott Mussoorie Walnut Grove Resort &amp; Spa<\/h4><p data-start=\"1594\" data-end=\"1894\"><em data-start=\"1648\" data-end=\"1671\">Barlowganj, Mussoorie<\/em><br data-start=\"1671\" data-end=\"1674\" \/>One of Mussoorie\u2019s most premium stays, about 5 km from Mall Road. The resort offers big valley views, indoor pool, multiple restaurants, and lots of space for kids. Rooms are modern with all comforts and large windows.<\/p><p data-start=\"1897\" data-end=\"1954\"><strong data-start=\"1897\" data-end=\"1909\">Best for<\/strong>: Families, honeymooners, special occasions<br \/><strong data-start=\"1957\" data-end=\"1973\">Approx Price<\/strong>: \u20b918,000\u2013\u20b930,000\/night<br \/><strong data-start=\"2001\" data-end=\"2017\">Good to Know<\/strong>: Great for longer stays (2\u20133 nights); check for meal packages<\/p><h4 data-start=\"1897\" data-end=\"1954\">Namah Resort, Jim Corbett<\/h4><p data-start=\"1897\" data-end=\"1954\"><em data-start=\"2120\" data-end=\"2148\">Dhikuli, near Bijrani Zone<\/em><br data-start=\"2148\" data-end=\"2151\" \/>Located just 8 km from Ramnagar, this is a comfortable, full-service resort near Corbett National Park. It has lawns, a pool, spa, and large rooms\u2014some with river views. Ideal if you want luxury near safari zones.<\/p><p data-start=\"2369\" data-end=\"2427\"><strong data-start=\"2369\" data-end=\"2381\">Best for<\/strong>: Wildlife lovers, seniors, relaxed holidays<br \/><strong data-start=\"2430\" data-end=\"2446\">Approx Price<\/strong>: \u20b99,000\u2013\u20b916,000\/night<br \/><strong data-start=\"2473\" data-end=\"2489\">Good to Know<\/strong>: Safaris need to be pre-booked; resort can help with that<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/details>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b9b0583 elementor-skin-carousel elementor-arrows-yes elementor-pagination-type-bullets elementor-pagination-position-outside elementor-widget elementor-widget-media-carousel\" data-id=\"b9b0583\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;slides_per_view&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;slides_per_view_mobile&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;slides_to_scroll&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;slides_to_scroll_mobile&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;space_between&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:25,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;space_between_m